attribute-definition.description:
JSON object based on OrderAddressMap Variable, specific values will vary by return service. EX: {
			"name" : '', 
			"city" : '',
			"stateCode" : '',
			"postalCode" : '',
			"countryCode" : '',
			"address1" : '',
			"address2" : '',
			"phone" : ''
		};

JWT signing key ID. It is required for the JWT header. 
	Example - jwtHeader: {
					alg: 'HS512',
					kid: '32b681ab-96e3-4181-90b6-54f0908c0a2b' // JWT Signing Key ID
				}
